Language file generation manual

1. Run "make" in the directory, to generate xml analyze tool.
2. Execute "./str_gen.sh <locale>", collecting the key words in source codes and configuration files, generating "<locale>.po".
3. Translate the key words in "<locale>.po", type the translated string in "msgstr".
4. Execute "./mo_gen.sh <locale>", generating the language file .mo, modify <locale> to any locale needed, e.g. "zh", "en", "jp".
5. Run makefile in mstudio folder to install the language file.
